text:
What is the rationale behind the hs editor nuking transitions? I’m talking about this code injection in the editor
```:not(.slick-track):not(.slick-slide):not(.hs-allow-transition):not([data-transition-wrapper]) {
  -webkit-transition: none!important;
  -moz-transition: none!important;
  -o-transition: none!important;
  -ms-transition: none!important;
  transition: none!important;
}```
